title: #268 - Edmund Husserl Pt. 1: Biography and Background
itunes:title: #268 - Edmund Husserl Pt. 1: Biography and Background
description: Strap in, folks! We're about to go deep on our boy Edmund Husserl (aka Eddy Hoos.) (aka Ed Casserole) (aka the Father of Phenomenology). This first episode takes a look at Husserl's biography, his educational background, and the philosophical runway that was laid before him at the start of the 20th century. Where my Cartesians at? Here, I hope.
